%   Xf = 2x1 cell 2, final 1 input delay states.
%   Each Xf{1,ts} = 12xQ matrix, final states for input #1.
%   Each Xf{2,ts} = 1xQ matrix, final states for input #2.
%
%   Af = 2x0 cell 2, final 0 layer delay states.
